{"tid":2449422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拆連登神台] 川普：如中國武力犯台，美國無能為力","createTime":"2021-03-16T15:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T02:13:07.000Z","uid":52658,"like":8,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f825519a182ee2227240e7eba3a25fd07630bf05","tid":2449422,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZxYN9Po.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxYN9Po.png&h=f77b0ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國前總統川普對於兩岸的立場常被視為「抗中」、「挺台」，但他個人想法可能並非如此，《華盛頓郵報》專欄作家羅金（Josh Rogin）最近出版的新書《天國下的混亂》（Chaos Under Heaven，暫譯）揭露川普私下被問到中國武力犯台，川普毫無護台意願，他說美國離中國太遠，「什麼都不能做。」書中指出，川普執政期間美國「友台」「挺台」政策，要歸功外交團隊而非川普本人。<br />\n<br />\n羅金的新書今天（16日）發售，新聞網站「野獸日報」昨搶先刊出書摘，書中主要是川普這四年跟中國交手的經過，川普根本沒興趣承諾保衛台灣對抗中國進犯，跟過去歷任美國總統立場不同。如果川普當時的言談被解讀為美國政策轉變，將對台灣造成不小的影響。<br />\n<br />\n羅金新書引述這段談話是2019年川普與一名共和黨籍參議員的私下對話，<span class=\"red\">這名參議員想說服川普出手阻止中國粗暴打壓香港民主抗爭</span>，參議員說，如放任中國更加膽大妄為，下一步就是拿下台灣，這對於川普將是一個汙點。<br />\n<br />\n但川普的回應讓參議員傻眼，川普說：「台灣距離中國大概只有2英呎」「而我們大概在8千英哩外，如果他們犯台，<span class=\"red\">我們xx的什麼都不能做</span>。」"},{"pid":"2ac0e9cb5c43860e92a3fdc743f068de5b058694","tid":2449422,"uid":48083,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"出書既就算啦<br />\n侵侵咁多親家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8f71f2b9aa2a45352b6ceb149f762c7af0e3c4","tid":2449422,"uid":137248,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"侵打句tweet夠收中共皮啦我地連登仔話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5663d83cd146ab2143cee8515bbd0840316f43f1","tid":2449422,"uid":370061,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:02:15.000Z","msg":"華盛頓郵報<br />\n啱啱先證實咗放fakenews屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b89f43d894d50617497e582e95692fbedce8a1","tid":2449422,"uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:02:19.000Z","msg":"美國國務院亞太副助卿黃之翰（Alex Wong）來台訪問，成為《台灣旅行法》通過後首位訪台高級外交官。他在台會見政府高官，演說時盛讚台灣是民主典範，並表示「美國是台灣緊密夥伴」，北京又向美國抗議。<br />\n<br />\n羅金書中寫道，川普聽說北京抗議後怒吼：「<span class=\"red\">XX的黃之翰是誰？</span>」「他要去台灣怎麼沒人告訴我，把他轟出去！」美國國務院並沒有開除黃之翰，但官員都明白川普意思了，接下來很久，美國政府沒有官員訪台。"},{"pid":"576f89d5d9ca2c009b4b2d8be96314408b6b087e","tid":2449422,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5663d83cd146ab2143cee8515bbd0840316f43f1","tid":2449422,"uid":370061,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:02:15.000Z","msg":"華盛頓郵報<br />\n啱啱先證實咗放fakenews屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:03:50.000Z","msg":"如果呢段對話係2017年講 我會信<br />\n但佢話係2019年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要再觀察下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係流料 川普一定告到佢褲甩"},{"pid":"55624d831a09bbf548a5513852de8e1a5cd4c51b","tid":2449422,"uid":378134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LKU9DKJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLKU9DKJ.gif&h=8950c1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smf1uRq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsmf1uRq.gif&h=e108f238&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"952872f124950c602e3f9eeda44983c832986cbf","tid":2449422,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3356306de57aea516e179d40c88a825b19d84589","tid":2449422,"uid":31520,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"cite