,"msg":"中國武力犯台<br />\n最大隱憂係驚好似當年8國聯軍咁樣<br />\n雖然好多大國都有唔少問題<br />\n但係一講到分餅仔同做正義撚<br />\n班撚樣肯定衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f196e0e2fbe8b249d47863f64267b95b9d005ec","tid":2449422,"uid":384679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3356306de57aea516e179d40c88a825b19d84589","tid":2449422,"uid":31520,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"Trump係2020年先真正對支共醒覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"19年係話想支那自己搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54177eb746e36e53a96bd1d39b63350d7493b76","tid":2449422,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:50:52.000Z","msg":"唔信"},{"pid":"16facfcc089bbc5c674f85f409b245139e998cb7","tid":2449422,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47263b7121284a0292f754400fb6c7d845e4a796","tid":2449422,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"又係WSJ d fake news"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"WSJ?"},{"pid":"03d80edf56988ab23a7567a2bc2db397b34e9274","tid":2449422,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd1447d996aa4447b9416c8631f6ba2ec9a05f4","tid":2449422,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"可以岩都可以錯<br />\n岩既係美台距離的確係好遠，對比大陸朝發夕至，美國支援同反應都要時間，不過若然你冇心阻止既，就算盟友係你隔離你都可以唔幫手睇住佢死<br />\n錯既係，就算阻止唔到你出手，只要台灣唔會太快淪陷，美國一樣可以做到野，事實上太平洋艦隊要嚟都好快，最多係南海打交"},{"pid":"ce297be56aa7f5d45062a32a877be7dc54b0abc0","tid":2449422,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f825519a182ee2227240e7eba3a25fd07630bf05","tid":2449422,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZxYN9Po.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxYN9Po.png&h=f77b0ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國前總統川普對於兩岸的立場常被視為「抗中」、「挺台」，但他個人想法可能並非如此，《華盛頓郵報》專欄作家羅金（Josh Rogin）最近出版的新書《天國下的混亂》（Chaos Under Heaven，暫譯）揭露川普私下被問到中國武力犯台，川普毫無護台意願，他說美國離中國太遠，「什麼都不能做。」書中指出，川普執政期間美國「友台」「挺台」政策，要歸功外交團隊而非川普本人。<br />\n<br />\n羅金的新書今天（16日）發售，新聞網站「野獸日報」昨搶先刊出書摘，書中主要是川普這四年跟中國交手的經過，川普根本沒興趣承諾保衛台灣對抗中國進犯，跟過去歷任美國總統立場不同。如果川普當時的言談被解讀為美國政策轉變，將對台灣造成不小的影響。<br />\n<br />\n羅金新書引述這段談話是2019年川普與一名共和黨籍參議員的私下對話，<span class=\"red\">這名參議員想說服川普出手阻止中國粗暴打壓香港民主抗爭</span>，參議員說，如放任中國更加膽大妄為，下一步就是拿下台灣，這對於川普將是一個汙點。<br />\n<br />\n但川普的回應讓參議員傻眼，川普說：「台灣距離中國大概只有2英呎」「而我們大概在8千英哩外，如果他們犯台，<span class=\"red\">我們xx的什麼都不能做</span>。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />made up quotes by WaPo<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0alwstDzmVY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0alwstDzmVY&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=830212e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0alwstDzmVY</a>"},{"pid":"b2e336a1c3615a06bd112e06e00bd567d9945854","tid":2449422,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1442bd8849fbe1f6794b11ca545087c67676d8e6","tid":2449422,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:27:16.000Z","msg":"花與愛麗絲呢條5 毛成撚日帶風向都有咁多連登傻仔吹奏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980ffebb8bbbd8adbc35ee1650752c22be0bf5d3","tid":2449422,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33aad5c607673989d1ecdf4297f34e5c30d15ef3","tid":2449422,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bdb6336d9a72e45ca0e80a7c97386f64f525dbb","tid":2449422,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:51:04.000Z","msg"